Starmap is a comprehensive AI model catalog system that provides
information about AI models, their capabilities, and providers.
It includes an embedded catalog of models that can be accessed offline,
as well as the ability to fetch live model information from provider APIs
completion Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell
export Export models in OpenAI or OpenRouter format
fetch Fetch live models from a provider API
list List all models from embedded catalog
sync Sync models from provider APIs to the embedded catalog
testdata Manage test data files for provider API responses
validate Validate provider API key configuration
Use "starmap [command] --help" for more information about a command.
